name: SBC Public Health
tweet: Vacúnese incluso si ha tenido COVID-19. Según los CDC, los sobrevivientes de COVID-19 que permanecieron sin vacunar tenían 5 veces más probabilidades de volver a infectarse que las personas completamente vacunadas que nunca se habían infectado:  https://t.co/IR2wYtKeRR  https://t.co/kO2WKJZ31C

name: SBC Public Health
tweet: People who have recovered from COVID-19 should get immunized, too. A CDC study showed COVID-19 survivors who remained unvaccinated were 5 times more likely to get a new coronavirus infection than fully vaccinated people who had never been infected:  https://t.co/IR2wYtKeRR  https://t.co/BxEQ8WR8nI
